&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;216&quot; data-end=&quot;234&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;216&quot; data-end=&quot;234&quot;&gt;About LumiMeds&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;251&quot; data-end=&quot;466&quot;&gt;LumiMeds is a fast-growing U.S.-based telehealth startup focused on weight management and long-term metabolic health. We are building the next generation of e-commerce and clinical infrastructure from the ground up.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;468&quot; data-end=&quot;684&quot;&gt;As an early-stage company, we move quickly, operate with limited layers, and expect high ownership from every team member. There is no bureaucracy here — decisions happen fast, priorities evolve, and builders thrive.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;686&quot; data-end=&quot;834&quot;&gt;We are a remote-first, globally distributed team that values clarity, accountability, and people who take initiative rather than wait for direction.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;LumiMeds is a fast-growing telehealth company in the compounded GLP-1 and metabolic health space. We&#39;re building a brand that actually connects with people, and we need a writer who knows how to make them laugh.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is not a &quot;write captions&quot; role. You&#39;ll be the creative engine behind our short-form comedy content, writing scripts for TikTok and Instagram Reels that are sharp, on-brand, and genuinely funny. You&#39;ll work closely with our Social Media Manager and on-camera talent to develop concepts, punch up hooks, and turn wellness topics into content people actually want to watch.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The right person for this role understands the rhythm of short-form comedy. You know how to land a joke in 15 seconds, write for a specific voice, and make a GLP-1 medication brand feel human without crossing compliance lines.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write scripts and concepts for short-form comedy content across TikTok and Instagram Reels&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop recurring formats, characters, and comedic angles rooted in the wellness and weight loss space&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the Creative Director and Social Media Manager on content calendars, hooks, and creative direction&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write for specific on-camera talent, adapting to their voice, timing, and delivery style&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ideate and pitch new concepts weekly, kill what doesn&#39;t land, build on what does&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work within FDA and FTC compliance guidelines for healthcare content (we&#39;ll train you, but you have to be open to it)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optionally appear on camera if you&#39;re comfortable, but not required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you won&#39;t do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role has clear scope boundaries, both to protect the brand and keep content compliant:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will NOT write scripts that make efficacy claims, weight-loss promises, or outcome guarantees about LumiMeds products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will NOT write testimonial-style content attributing personal results to medications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will NOT write content that compares LumiMeds compounded medications to FDA-approved branded products in promotional terms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we&#39;re looking for&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A portfolio of short-form comedy writing. Spec scripts, published content, personal account, anything that shows you can be funny in under 60 seconds&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of TikTok and Reels formats, trends, and what makes content perform&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to write for someone else

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;216&quot; data-end=&quot;234&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;216&quot; data-end=&quot;234&quot;&gt;About LumiMeds&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;251&quot; data-end=&quot;466&quot;&gt;LumiMeds is a fast-growing U.S.-based telehealth startup focused on weight management and long-term metabolic health. We are building the next generation of e-commerce and clinical infrastructure from the ground up.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;468&quot; data-end=&quot;684&quot;&gt;As an early-stage company, we move quickly, operate with limited layers, and expect high ownership from every team member. There is no bureaucracy here — decisions happen fast, priorities evolve, and builders thrive.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;686&quot; data-end=&quot;834&quot;&gt;We are a remote-first, globally distributed team that values clarity, accountability, and people who take initiative rather than wait for direction.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;LumiMeds is a fast-growing telehealth company in the compounded GLP-1 and metabolic health space. We&#39;re building a brand people actually trust, and we need someone to grow it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is not a &quot;post and pray&quot; role. You&#39;ll be the face and engine behind our social channels, creating content that stops the scroll, builds an audience, and drives real growth on TikTok and Instagram. You&#39;ll work closely with our Social Media Manager on scripts, concepts, and hooks, then bring them to life on camera with the kind of energy that actually makes people watch.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The right person for this role has a UGC and paid ad background, knows what makes short-form content convert, and is genuinely compelling on camera. Not just comfortable. Compelling.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Appear on camera regularly across Reels, TikToks, trends, talking head, and storytelling formats&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with the Social Media Manager on scripts, concepts, and hooks before filming&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and test content formats fast. Kill what doesn&#39;t work, double down on what does&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Produce UGC-style and paid ad content that converts across the funnel&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track performance weekly and connect content decisions to growth metrics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay ahead of platform trends and bring native ideas to the table&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate on campaign moments, product launches, and patient stories&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you won&#39;t do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role has clear scope boundaries, both to protect the brand and keep content compliant:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will NOT make efficacy claims, weight-loss promises, or outcome guarantees about LumiMeds products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will NOT create testimonial-style content attributing personal results to medications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will NOT compare LumiMeds compounded medications to FDA-approved branded products in promotional terms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we&#39;re looking for&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record of growing a brand or personal account. We want to see numbers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong UGC and paid ad content background&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Naturally engaging on camera. Not just comfortable, actually compelling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fast executor. You can go from concept to posted in hours, not days&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong instinct for short-form video: hooks, pacing, captions, all of it&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reliable home production setup (phone camera, decent lighting, quiet space)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willingness to work within FDA marketing comp

