&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot;&gt;Lumi is looking for a Copywriter&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;who can craft clear, persuasive, and compliant copy that feels genuine and engaging—not like a robot or a pharma brochure! We are specifically looking for a talented writer based in&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;Latin America, South America, or Europe&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;who has a proven track record of writing for&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;US-based e-commerce or healthcare brands.&lt;/p&gt;
