&lt;p&gt;You will own the relationship with our existing patient base — proactively engaging subscribers before they disengage, handling cancellation and pause requests, and identifying the moments where a patient needs a nudge, a reframe, or a real conversation to stay committed to their care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is not a reactive churn queue. You&#39;ll reach out before the cancel request comes in, identify at-risk patients through behavioral signals, and build the kind of trust that makes patients want to stay. You&#39;ll need empathy, persistence, and the ability to have honest conversations about health commitments — not just subscription logistics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Actually Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
